  Source:
    Title: The Book of Hours
    Locus: I 45
  Locus:
    Daily: December 28
Format: Verse
Title: Wheel of God
---
You are a wheel at which I stand,
whose dark spokes sometimes catch me up,
revolve me nearer to the center.
Then all the work I put my hand to
widens from turn to turn.
